body:
@Nott If it is a deadlock then `kill -QUIT` the rclone process and collect the backtrace, or use [this procedure](https://rclone.org/rc/#debugging-go-routine-leaks) via the rc.

If you want more help then please make a new issue with that in :-)

Note glusterfs is weird... Its nanosecond timestamps aren't consistent which could conceivably mess with rclone so using `--modify-window` might be a good idea.
